COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x15a
STRING: I had been feeling restless ever since what happened
yesterday.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x170
STRING: If I opened the door in front of me, I would see Fal
there.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x17c
STRING: She would say good morning, and smile.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x188
STRING: This would surely continue until the graduation recital
was over.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x19e
STRING: I hadn't abandoned everything just yet, so it was hard
for me to honestly feel happy with this.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1b4
STRING: But, standing here in front of the practice room door,
and imagining who was there on the other side made
my heart begin to race, and I couldn't resist my
feelings.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1d4
STRING: I took a deep breath, put on a straight face, and opened
the door to the practice room.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x22a
STRING: [Chris] “Morning.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x240
STRING: Saying this as I entered the room, I didn't get the
response I had imagined I would, and suddenly I felt
disappointed.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x256
STRING: [Chris] “...She's not here yet?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x26c
STRING: It was still five minutes before our agreed meeting time.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x278
STRING: But usually, Fal was always here earlier than I was.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x28e
STRING: I decided to begin setting up my Fortelle and score
before being asked to.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2a4
STRING: I placed the pages of my score on my lap, and put them
back into order as they had gotten messed up in my
bag, and vividly recalled what happened yesterday.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2dc
STRING: At that moment-

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x304
STRING: If her score hadn't fallen to the floor by chance like
that...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x310
STRING: Would I have just gone and kissed her?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x31c
STRING: The answer to that question was quite clear.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x32a
STRING: It was just the result of coincidences overlapping in
which there were no facts, and my heart had already
given its answer.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x342
STRING: So, I continued telling myself my excuses.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x350
STRING: Arie had known me better than I knew myself...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x35c
STRING: She had accurately understood what was going to
happen.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x368
STRING: And the answer she had found to this, was to break up
with me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x376
STRING: And at the end of her letter, she had written this:

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x390
STRING: “Forgive me.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3e0
STRING: [Fal] “Oh, good morning, Chris.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3f6
STRING: [Chris] “...Morning. It's rare for you to arrive after me.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x41e
STRING: [Fal] “I was talking to Ms. Cordell. She said she is doing
one last check up on all her students, since everything
will be over after this week.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x450
STRING: [Fal] “And, that she wants to listen to us play at
midday.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x466
STRING: [Chris] “Why did she choose to tell you... Could it be
that she doesn't trust me?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4a2
STRING: [Fal] “Aha-ha.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4d0
STRING: I just happened to be passing by her
office, that's all.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4dc
STRING: [Chris] “You had something to do over in the First Hall?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x50e
STRING: [Fal] “Hm? Oh, more or less. One of the teachers asked
me to help them...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x52e
STRING: [Chris] “What? Copying a score again or something?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x560
STRING: [Fal] “Bingo.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x576
STRING: [Chris] “At a time like this?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5a8
STRING: [Fal] “But it's just five pages.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5be
STRING: [Chris] “The volume isn't the problem.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5f0
STRING: [Fal] “I finish work earlier now, right? I just have to
spend a little time on it before going to bed and it'll be
done.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x610
STRING: [Chris] “Kind of feels like it defeats the purpose of you
having your shifts shortened...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x64c
STRING: [Fal] “I-It's okay, really.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x67a
STRING: They consider all this when they
ask me, and trust that I'll be okay.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x690
STRING: [Chris] “＊sigh＊ I can't tell if you're too diligent, or
just...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6c2
STRING: [Fal] “I think I was just born this way, so I've given up
fighting it.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6d8
STRING: [Chris] “If you put it that way, then there's nothing more
for me to say, but... I could've helped you, you know?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x714
STRING: [Fal] “Really? I should've asked you to.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x72a
STRING: [Chris] “Really. I've never said no in the past, have I?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x766
STRING: [Fal] “That's true. Okay, next time I might ask you, then.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x77c
STRING: [Chris] “No... Just say no to them next time.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x7ae
STRING: [Fal] “Ugh...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x7d8
STRING: We both started laughing, and I felt thankful from the
bottom of my heart that it didn't turn awkward.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x7ee
STRING: Fal's attitude didn't show any signs that she was forcing
herself not to think about what happened yesterday.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x804
STRING: It seemed that she had accepted it, and was smiling
naturally regardless.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x81a
STRING: Our relationship had obviously begun to change.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x826
STRING: I don't think I would try to avoid Fal because of Arie.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x83c
STRING: I should just plain admit it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x848
STRING: I had developed feelings for Fal.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8ac
STRING: [Cordell] “Well then, shall we get straight down to
business?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8cc
STRING: Ms. Cordell was her usual self, concisely telling us only
what she wanted us to do.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8e2
STRING: We had already rehearsed a little, so my body was
feeling quite limber.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8f8
STRING: [Chris] “I'm good to start any time.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x92a
STRING: [Fal] “So am I.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x954
STRING: Ms. Cordell showed a slight expression of surprise
towards my response, and then smiled.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x96a
STRING: [Chris] “...Is something the matter?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x988
STRING: [Cordell] “No, why, I was just thinking that those words
were a rarity for you.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x99e
STRING: [Chris] “...Is it really that rare?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x9d0
STRING: [Cordell] “Normally you would have said something like,
‘I'm ready, more or less.’”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa0c
STRING: [Fal] “Aha-ha.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa22
STRING: [Chris] “...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa40
STRING: [Cordell] “I am just teasing you.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa6e
STRING: ...But I suppose it is
true.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa92
STRING: Either way, do not concern yourself.
Now, why don't you begin?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xaa8
STRING: [Chris] “＊sigh＊”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xabe
STRING: It wasn't like I was unaware of the change in my
mentality, but having it pointed out to my face made me
want to retort a little.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xafa
STRING: [Cordell] “I truly am sorry. Now, if you do not start soon
it will put me in a difficult spot, too. I still have a lot of
students to check on.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb24
STRING: [Chris] “Yes, Ms. Cordell.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb3a
STRING: I had just heard one of the wonders of the world, an
apology from Ms. Cordell, and it also seemed that she
really was in a difficult place,

COMMANDS.LABEL: b3a
STRING: so I stopped being childish and placed my fingers
on my Fortelle.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbd8
STRING: We finished performing for Ms. Cordell, and our
ensemble had gone so well that even I was satisfied
with it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc14
STRING: [Cordell] “...Yes, I see now.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc2a
STRING: She looked like she had something else to say, but Ms.
Cordell said only this, and then stared at me for a short
time.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc4a
STRING: [Chris] “Umm... Is something the matter?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc68
STRING: [Cordell] “Hm? Oh, it's nothing.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc7e
STRING: [Chris] “＊sigh＊”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc94
STRING: In any case, our rehearsals for today weren't over yet.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xca0
STRING: When I turned around to look at Fal, our gazes met as
she was staring at me with the same expression on her
face that Ms. Cordell had.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcde
STRING: Perhaps my fingers were getting tired, as I wasn't
entirely satisfied with the way I had just played.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcf4
STRING: I wasn't expecting that the last rehearsal we would
show Ms. Cordell would turn out this way...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd0a
STRING: [Chris] “...Sorry, something doesn't feel quite right.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd3c
STRING: [Cordell] “Well, that's fine, but...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd52
STRING: [Chris] “I'm sorry?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd84
STRING: [Cordell] “Oh, nothing. You are fortunate this isn't your
graduation recital.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd9a
STRING: [Chris] “Yes, I agree.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xdb8
STRING: [Cordell] “As long as you understand. I have no
intention of telling you to try hard at this point. If you
cannot put everything you have into your graduation
recital, then that is where it will all end.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xdd8
STRING: [Chris] “...Yes, Ms. Cordell.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xdee
STRING: Compared to the way Fal sang, it was me who was
making the mistakes.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xdfa
STRING: I took Ms. Cordell's words to heart, and then turned to
face Fal.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe10
STRING: [Chris] “I'll be fine when it comes to the recital.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe42
STRING: [Fal] “...Huh?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe58
STRING: [Chris] “Fal...?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe8a
STRING: [Fal] “Oh, yes?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xea0
STRING: [Chris] “I wasn't actually asking you anything. Are you
okay?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xed2
STRING: [Fal] “Yes, I'm fine. Well, shall we get ready to head
home?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xef4
STRING: I ended up going with the flow that Fal forced upon me,
and nodded.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf00
STRING: Following her lead, I also began to pack up my Fortelle.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf32
STRING: [Fal] “Okay then, thank you very much for today.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf48
STRING: [Chris] “Thank you.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf7a
STRING: [Cordell] “You do not have much time left. Be sure to
make the most of it.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf90
STRING: [Chris] “...Yes, we know.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfae
STRING: [Cordell] “There should be no problem, as long as you
understand.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfc4
STRING: [Chris] “Okay, okay.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfe2
STRING: [Fal] “...If you'll excuse us.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1018
STRING: [Cordell] “Chris.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x102e
STRING: Ms. Cordell stopped me, just as Fal left ahead of me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1044
STRING: [Chris] “Yes?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1076
STRING: [Cordell] “Did something happen?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x108c
STRING: [Chris] “...Yes, a lot of things, I suppose.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10be
STRING: [Cordell] “I see... Very well.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10d4
STRING: [Chris] “＊sigh＊ Okay then. Oh, that's right. Have your
heard anything from Asino about his partner?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x111a
STRING: [Cordell] “Yes. He is next, actually. He found a recital
partner. He does not have a lot of time left, but knowing
Asino, he should be okay. He is smart, and
flexible.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1144
STRING: [Chris] “I see. That's a relief to hear. Well, if you'll
excuse me.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11bc
STRING: [Fal] “Is everything okay?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11d2
STRING: Fal was standing in front of the door, and it seemed that
she was concerned why I came out late, and asked me
about it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11e8
STRING: [Chris] “Yeah. Ms. Cordell just stopped me to ask me
something.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1206
STRING: [Fal] “...What did she ask you about?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x121c
STRING: [Chris] “If something had happened or not. That's all.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x124e
STRING: [Fal] “Oh... It seems like you were in there a long time
for such a simple question.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x126e
STRING: [Chris] “I asked her about Asino. Apparently he was able
to find himself a partner. I was a little worried, but Ms.
Cordell said he'd be okay.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x12b4
STRING: [Fal] “Oh, I see. That's good to hear.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x12ca
STRING: [Chris] “Yeah.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x12fc
STRING: [Fal] “Oh, by the way, what are you doing today?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1312
STRING: [Chris] “What do you mean? Aren't we going to keep
practicing?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1330
STRING: [Fal] “I meant after that. Would you like to come over
for dinner? Your place is okay too, though.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1350
STRING: [Chris] “I...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1382
STRING: [Fal] “...Don't want to?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1398
STRING: [Chris] “...Don't have any problem with that.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13ca
STRING: [Fal] “It's decided, then.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13f8
STRING: Since we went to your place
last time... Why don't we eat at mine tonight?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x140e
STRING: [Chris] “I don't mind either way.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1440
STRING: [Fal] “That's also decided, then. So, shall we finish up a
little earlier than usual today?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1460
STRING: [Chris] “We probably shouldn't...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1492
STRING: [Fal] “Well now, that's not like you...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14c0
STRING: But you're right.
Dinner will taste better if we practice hard, anyway.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14d6
STRING: [Chris] “If... You say so. Can't help but raise an eyebrow
at the first part, though.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1512
STRING: [Fal] “Aha-ha!”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1528
STRING: Fal let out an honest laugh, and we walked toward the
practice rooms.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x153e
STRING: Watching her as she walked ahead of me, I couldn't
keep the feelings of happiness at bay.
